---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="How This Works — The Fourth Angle">
  <div style="max-width:640px;margin:0 auto;">
    <header style="padding:16px 18px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;">
      <a href="/" style="font-size:14px;color:#495057;text-decoration:none;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;min-height:44px;">
        <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="15 18 9 12 15 6"/></svg>
        Back
      </a>
      <div style="flex:1;"></div>
      <img src="/logo.png?v=2" alt="" style="height:24px;width:auto;" />
    </header>
    <article style="padding:20px 18px;max-width:640px;">
      <section style="margin-bottom:32px;">
        <h1 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:24px;font-weight:800;color:var(--text-primary);margin:0 0 14px 0;letter-spacing:-0.02em;line-height:1.2;">On any Malaysian issue, there are three angles: the government's, the opposition's, and the mob's. All three are shaped by political incentive. We provide the fourth.</h1>
        <p style="font-size:15px;line-height:1.72;color:var(--text-secondary);margin:0 0 14px 0;">The Fourth Angle is a non-partisan Malaysian issues platform. We do not tell you what to think. We show you what every side left out — then let you decide.</p>
        <p style="font-size:15px;line-height:1.72;color:var(--text-secondary);margin:0;">Every issue is fact-checked, bias-measured across 12 dimensions, stress-tested for cowardice, and published with the full audit visible. If we are biased, you can see exactly where and by how much.</p>
      </section>

      <section style="margin-bottom:28px;">
        <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:19px;font-weight:600;color:var(--text-primary);margin:0 0 10px 0;">How It Works</h2>
        <p style="font-size:15px;line-height:1.72;color:var(--text-primary);margin:0 0 14px 0;">Every issue goes through 6 independent editorial stages designed to catch what the others miss. Each stage challenges the one before it. The final output is scored, measured, and published with full audit transparency.</p>
        <p style="font-size:15px;line-height:1.72;color:var(--text-primary);margin:0;">No Malaysian outlet publishes its bias measurements. We do.</p>
      </section>

      <!-- Verdict Bar explanation -->
      <section style="margin-bottom:28px;">
        <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:19px;font-weight:600;color:var(--text-primary);margin:0 0 10px 0;">The Verdict Bar</h2>
        <p style="font-size:15px;line-height:1.72;color:var(--text-primary);margin:0 0 14px 0;">Every issue shows how each editorial stage assessed it.</p>
        <!-- Example verdict bar -->
        <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:0;padding:10px 14px;background:var(--amber-bg);border:1px solid rgba(44,34,21,0.05);border-radius:12px;margin-bottom:14px;">
          <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;flex:1;">
            <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:3px;">
              <div style="width:10px;height:10px;border-radius:50%;background:#2B8A3E;box-shadow:0 0 0 2px #EBFBEE;"></div>
              <span style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:8px;font-weight:600;color:var(--text-tertiary);letter-spacing:0.04em;">PA</span>
            </div>
            <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:3px;">
              <div style="width:10px;height:10px;border-radius:50%;background:#B85C00;box-shadow:0 0 0 2px #FFF4E6;"></div>
              <span style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:8px;font-weight:600;color:var(--text-tertiary);letter-spacing:0.04em;">BA</span>
            </div>
            <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:3px;">
              <div style="width:10px;height:10px;border-radius:50%;background:#2B8A3E;box-shadow:0 0 0 2px #EBFBEE;"></div>
              <span style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:8px;font-weight:600;color:var(--text-tertiary);letter-spacing:0.04em;">FC</span>
            </div>
            <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:3px;">
              <div style="width:10px;height:10px;border-radius:50%;background:#2B8A3E;box-shadow:0 0 0 2px #EBFBEE;"></div>
              <span style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:8px;font-weight:600;color:var(--text-tertiary);letter-spacing:0.04em;">AF</span>
            </div>
            <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:3px;">
              <div style="width:10px;height:10px;border-radius:50%;background:#B85C00;box-shadow:0 0 0 2px #FFF4E6;"></div>
              <span style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:8px;font-weight:600;color:var(--text-tertiary);letter-spacing:0.04em;">CT</span>
            </div>
            <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:3px;">
              <div style="width:10px;height:10px;border-radius:50%;background:#2B8A3E;box-shadow:0 0 0 2px #EBFBEE;"></div>
              <span style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:8px;font-weight:600;color:var(--text-tertiary);letter-spacing:0.04em;">SR</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div style="display:flex;align-items:baseline;gap:4px;margin-left:12px;">
            <span style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:16px;font-weight:700;color:var(--text-primary);">78</span>
            <span style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:10px;font-weight:500;color:var(--text-tertiary);">/100</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:6px;font-size:13px;color:var(--text-secondary);line-height:1.5;">
          <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;">
            <div style="width:8px;height:8px;border-radius:50%;background:#2B8A3E;flex-shrink:0;"></div>
            Balanced — stage found no significant issues
          </div>
          <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;">
            <div style="width:8px;height:8px;border-radius:50%;background:#B85C00;flex-shrink:0;"></div>
            Flagged — stage found moderate concerns
          </div>
          <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;">
            <div style="width:8px;height:8px;border-radius:50%;background:#E03131;flex-shrink:0;"></div>
            Alert — stage found significant issues
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Opinion Shift explanation -->
      <section style="margin-bottom:28px;">
        <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:19px;font-weight:600;color:var(--text-primary);margin:0 0 10px 0;">Opinion Shift</h2>
        <p style="font-size:15px;line-height:1.72;color:var(--text-primary);margin:0 0 14px 0;">How much you'd miss by reading only the headline. Higher means more hidden complexity.</p>
        <!-- Example opinion bar -->
        <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;margin-bottom:14px;">
          <div style="flex:1;height:6px;background:#F1F3F5;border-radius:3px;overflow:hidden;">
            <div style="height:100%;width:76%;background:#B85C00;border-radius:3px;"></div>
          </div>
          <span style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:14px;font-weight:700;color:#B85C00;">76</span>
          <span style="font-size:11px;font-weight:600;color:#495057;">Significant</span>
        </div>
        <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:6px;">
          <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;padding:8px 10px;background:var(--card);border-radius:8px;">
            <span style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:#E03131;">80–100</span>
            <span style="font-size:12px;color:var(--text-secondary);">Fundamental</span>
          </div>
          <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;padding:8px 10px;background:var(--card);border-radius:8px;">
            <span style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:#B85C00;">60–79</span>
            <span style="font-size:12px;color:var(--text-secondary);">Significant</span>
          </div>
          <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;padding:8px 10px;background:var(--card);border-radius:8px;">
            <span style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:#1971C2;">40–59</span>
            <span style="font-size:12px;color:var(--text-secondary);">Partial</span>
          </div>
          <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;padding:8px 10px;background:var(--card);border-radius:8px;">
            <span style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:#6C757D;">0–39</span>
            <span style="font-size:12px;color:var(--text-secondary);">Surface</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section style="margin-bottom:28px;">
        <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:19px;font-weight:600;color:var(--text-primary);margin:0 0 10px 0;">The Six Stages</h2>
        <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:14px;">
          <div style="background:var(--card);border-radius:12px;padding:16px;border-left:3px solid var(--amber);">
            <h3 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:16px;font-weight:600;margin:0 0 4px 0;">1. Primary Analysis (PA)</h3>
            <p style="font-size:14px;color:var(--text-secondary);margin:0;line-height:1.6;">Six-card analysis from court documents, parliamentary records, and primary sources. Every sentence written knowing it will be audited across 12 dimensions.</p>
          </div>
          <div style="background:var(--card);border-radius:12px;padding:16px;border-left:3px solid var(--lens-social);">
            <h3 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:16px;font-weight:600;margin:0 0 4px 0;">2. Bias Audit (BA)</h3>
            <p style="font-size:14px;color:var(--text-secondary);margin:0;line-height:1.6;">Scans for 9 bias types — partisan, racial, religious, geographic, economic, gender, omission, emotional manipulation, and diplomatic evasion.</p>
          </div>
          <div style="background:var(--card);border-radius:12px;padding:16px;border-left:3px solid var(--lens-legal);">
            <h3 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:16px;font-weight:600;margin:0 0 4px 0;">3. Fact Verification (FC)</h3>
            <p style="font-size:14px;color:var(--text-secondary);margin:0;line-height:1.6;">Every claim verified against primary sources. Each gets a confidence score: verified, unverified, misleading, or incorrect.</p>
          </div>
          <div style="background:var(--card);border-radius:12px;padding:16px;border-left:3px solid var(--lens-economic);">
            <h3 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:16px;font-weight:600;margin:0 0 4px 0;">4. Alternative Framing (AF)</h3>
            <p style="font-size:14px;color:var(--text-secondary);margin:0;line-height:1.6;">Finds missing voices — B40, East Malaysia, women, youth, intra-community class divides. Counter-arguments the reader deserves to hear.</p>
          </div>
          <div style="background:var(--card);border-radius:12px;padding:16px;border-left:3px solid var(--lens-critical);">
            <h3 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:16px;font-weight:600;margin:0 0 4px 0;">5. Contrarian Stress-Test (CT)</h3>
            <p style="font-size:14px;color:var(--text-secondary);margin:0;line-height:1.6;">Attacks the analysis. Where is it cowardly? Where does it hedge when evidence is clear? Would a taxi driver in Ipoh feel spoken to or lectured at?</p>
          </div>
          <div style="background:var(--card);border-radius:12px;padding:16px;border-left:3px solid var(--amber-light);">
            <h3 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:16px;font-weight:600;margin:0 0 4px 0;">6. Synthesis Review (SR)</h3>
            <p style="font-size:14px;color:var(--text-secondary);margin:0;line-height:1.6;">Integrates all five critiques. Corrects facts first, then rebalances bias, fills gaps, strengthens courage. Produces the final score.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section style="margin-bottom:28px;">
        <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:19px;font-weight:600;color:var(--text-primary);margin:0 0 10px 0;">12 Bias Dimensions</h2>
        <p style="font-size:15px;line-height:1.72;color:var(--text-primary);margin:0 0 14px 0;">Every article is measured across all 12. The full vector is published on each issue.</p>
        <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:6px;">
          <span style="font-size:13px;color:var(--text-secondary);padding:6px 10px;background:var(--card);border-radius:8px;">Tone</span>
          <span style="font-size:13px;color:var(--text-secondary);padding:6px 10px;background:var(--card);border-radius:8px;">Political lean</span>
          <span style="font-size:13px;color:var(--text-secondary);padding:6px 10px;background:var(--card);border-radius:8px;">Ethnic framing</span>
          <span style="font-size:13px;color:var(--text-secondary);padding:6px 10px;background:var(--card);border-radius:8px;">Religious sensitivity</span>
          <span style="font-size:13px;color:var(--text-secondary);padding:6px 10px;background:var(--card);border-radius:8px;">Narrative framing</span>
          <span style="font-size:13px;color:var(--text-secondary);padding:6px 10px;background:var(--card);border-radius:8px;">Completeness</span>
          <span style="font-size:13px;color:var(--text-secondary);padding:6px 10px;background:var(--card);border-radius:8px;">Timing</span>
          <span style="font-size:13px;color:var(--text-secondary);padding:6px 10px;background:var(--card);border-radius:8px;">Certainty</span>
          <span style="font-size:13px;color:var(--text-secondary);padding:6px 10px;background:var(--card);border-radius:8px;">Source diversity</span>
          <span style="font-size:13px;color:var(--text-secondary);padding:6px 10px;background:var(--card);border-radius:8px;">Geographic balance</span>
          <span style="font-size:13px;color:var(--text-secondary);padding:6px 10px;background:var(--card);border-radius:8px;">Economic framing</span>
          <span style="font-size:13px;color:var(--text-secondary);padding:6px 10px;background:var(--card);border-radius:8px;">Gender agency</span>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section style="margin-bottom:28px;">
        <div style="background:var(--amber-bg);border:1px solid rgba(139,101,8,0.12);border-radius:12px;padding:18px;">
          <p style="font-size:14px;line-height:1.72;color:var(--text-primary);margin:0;font-style:italic;">We do not claim neutrality. We claim measurable balance across 12 published dimensions, verified factual accuracy, quantified inter-stage conflict, and radical transparency about our methodology and its limits.</p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section style="margin-bottom:28px;">
        <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:19px;font-weight:600;color:var(--text-primary);margin:0 0 10px 0;">Verify Authenticity</h2>
        <p style="font-size:15px;line-height:1.72;color:var(--text-primary);margin:0 0 14px 0;">Every issue carries a cryptographic fingerprint. Verify any content is authentic and unmodified.</p>
        <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:8px;margin-bottom:14px;">
          <a href="/verify.html" style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;font-size:14px;font-weight:600;color:var(--amber);text-decoration:none;">
            <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
            Open offline verifier
          </a>
          <a href="/pubkey.pem" style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;font-size:14px;font-weight:600;color:var(--amber);text-decoration:none;">
            <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="11" width="18" height="11" rx="2" ry="2"/><path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0110 0v4"/></svg>
            View public key
          </a>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section style="margin-bottom:28px;">
        <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:19px;font-weight:600;color:var(--text-primary);margin:0 0 10px 0;">Contact</h2>
        <a href="mailto:thefourthangle@proton.me" style="font-size:15px;line-height:1.72;color:#1971C2;text-decoration:none;">thefourthangle@proton.me</a>
      </section>

      <section style="margin-bottom:28px;">
        <a href="/disclaimer" style="font-size:13px;color:var(--text-tertiary);text-decoration:none;">Disclaimer & Legal Notice</a>
      </section>
    </article>
    <div style="height:40px;"></div>
  </div>
</Base>
